sudo set-hostname GoCd-Server
curl https://raw.githubusercontent.com/CodingManoj/rhel9-tools/refs/heads/main/GOCD/01-gocd-server-init.sh |sudo bash (by running these command we will get the )
In application disk space issue go through these commands
