### Creat a WS 
* In ws install the agent 
* [ ec2-user@WS ~ ]$ curl https://raw.githubusercontent.com/CodingManoj/      rhel9-tools/refs/heads/main/GOCD/02-gocd-agent-init.sh |sudo bash
