 -> Open this file /home/gocd/go-agent-23.5.0/wrapper-config/wrapper-properties.conf & Update wrapper.app.parameter.101 line and replace localhost with gocd server ip address and restart gocd-agent service
To restart service systemctl restart gocd-agent

